name: Tosh - Los Angelese
description: This was the second time I shot Tosh. First time we met at the beach and this time she invited me to her condo. Both times ended in a drunk me. The first time was a sunrise shoot and when we were done we went to the Circle K and got a couple of tall boys to hold us over until the bars opened up. Then we ended up drinking for free for a couple of hours. It obviously wasn't me that was attracting the free drinks but they still tasted the same:) After this shoot we went to a restaurant and what do you know, they had beer:) Tosh is another one of those home town girls that lives somewhere else now so it's only ever by luck we run into each other. Hopefully it happens again soon.
